    "schema": "Latin-Square study design. Each participant is assigned one order (1–4) via the URL parameter ?order=N. Every order presents all four conditions (SV0 baseline, SV1 categorical, SV2 numerical, SV3 directional) each paired with a different task type (Estimation, Structure, Browsing, Attribute).",
